  "text": [
    "Winter mornings",
    "driving past",
    "I\u2019d see these kids",
    "huddled like grouse",
    "in the plowed ruts",
    "in front of their shack",
    "waiting for the bus,",
    "three small children",
    "bunched against the drifts",
    "rising behind them.",
    "This morning",
    "I slowed to wave",
    "and the smallest,",
    "a stick of a kid",
    "draped in a coat,",
    "grinned and raised",
    "his red, raw hand,",
    "the snowball",
    "packed with rock",
    "aimed at my face."
  ],
  "title": "Back Road",
  "year": ""
}